Radular formula 30 × 10.1.1.1.10 (spc.TH81, H = 
6.5 mm
), 35 × 10.1.1.1.10 (spc. TH82, H = 
7 mm
). Rachidian tooth tricuspid, cusps triangular, with rounded tips; central cusp larger, lateral cusps reduced. Lateral teeth hook-shaped, smooth; inner lateral with broader cusp, outer laterals tapering outwardly.

